#: ../../source/janim/items/geometry/modules.rst:2
msgid "geometry"
msgstr "geometry"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:1 of
msgid "几何物件的基类"
msgstr "Base class for geometry items"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:3 of
msgid "提供了 :meth:`reshape` 通用方法与相关辅助函数"
msgstr "Provides the general :meth:`reshape` method and related helper functions"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:5 of
msgid "其中："
msgstr "Specifically:"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:7 of
msgid "``_reshape`` 用于最底层的几何物件实现"
msgstr "``_reshape`` is used for the lowest-level geometry item implementation"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:9 of
msgid "``reshape`` 用于给子类可以覆盖，可以用来改变外部的顶层行为"
msgstr "``reshape`` is intended to be overridden by subclasses, and can be used to change top-level external behavior"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:11 of
msgid ""
"（例如 :class:`~.Polygon` 默认是使用 ``verts`` 和 ``close_path`` 构造， 而 :class:`~.RegularPolygon` 覆盖 ``reshape`` 改"
"为 ``n``、``radius`` 和 ``start_angle`` 构造）"
msgstr ""
"(For example, :class:`~.Polygon` is built with ``verts`` and ``close_path`` by default, while :class:`~.RegularPolygon` "
"overrides ``reshape`` to build from ``n``, ``radius``, and ``start_angle``)"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape:14 of
msgid ""
"如果需要另行获取已记忆的参数值，比如获取 :class:`~.Star` 的 ``start_angle``， 可以直接使用例如 "
"``.reshape_params['start_angle']`` 的方式"
msgstr ""
"If you need to retrieve remembered parameter values separately, such as :class:`~.Star`'s ``start_angle``, you can "
"directly use forms like ``.reshape_params['start_angle']``"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape.reshape:1 of
msgid "类似传递给 ``__init__`` 的参数，重新设置几何物件的形状"
msgstr "Similar to passing parameters to ``__init__``, reset the shape of the geometry item"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape.reshape:3 of
msgid "可以缺省部分值，表示使用先前的；具体用法请参考 :ref:`geometry_reshape` 文档教程"
msgstr ""
"Some values can be omitted to reuse previous ones; for detailed usage, refer to the :ref:`geometry_reshape` tutorial"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape.copy:1 of
msgid "复制物件"
msgstr "Copy item"

#: janim.items.geometry.__init__.GeometryShape.become:1 of
msgid "将该物件的数据设置为与传入的物件相同（以复制的方式，不是引用）"
msgstr "Set this item's data to match the passed item (by copying, not by reference)"
